---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Group CSV by Column in the Browser - GigaSieve Guide" description="Use GigaSieve to group large CSVs by a column without Excel.">
    <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
        <nav class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">
            <a href="/guides" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Guides</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400">Group CSV by Column in the Browser</span>
        </nav>

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-200 mb-4">Group CSV by Column in the Browser</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
            Group-by is the fastest way to summarize large CSVs. GigaSieve can do it in the browser, locally.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Common use cases</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <li>Count orders per country</li>
                <li>Top customers by frequency</li>
                <li>Status distribution</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Steps</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <li>Open the CSV in /app.</li>
                <li>Select the column to group by.</li>
                <li>Check the counts in the Insights panel.</li>
                <li>Export the summary if needed.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="/app" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-8">
            Try GigaSieve ->
        </a>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Related</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="/guides/open-1gb-csv-in-browser" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Open 1GB CSV in Browser</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/guides/why-csv-is-slow" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Why CSV is Slow</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/recipes/csv/group-by" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Group By (CSV)</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/recipes/csv/top-values" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Column Top Values</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
